      <p class="text-xs text-mute leading-relaxed">
        The health-related calculators, nutritional estimates, diet plans, meal suggestions, fitness recommendations, and wellness information available on WHealth Calculator are provided solely for educational and informational purposes. They do not constitute medical advice, diagnosis, treatment, or individualized healthcare recommendations.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-mute leading-relaxed font-semibold">
        Always consult a qualified physician, registered dietitian, certified nutritionist, or other licensed healthcare professional before starting or modifying any diet, exercise program, bodybuilding routine, weight-loss plan, medication, or other healthcare regimen. Never disregard or delay seeking professional medical advice because of information obtained from WHealth Calculator.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 bg-canvas-soft-2 border border-hairline rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-ink flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-warning"></span>
        3. Financial Disclaimer
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-mute leading-relaxed">
        The financial calculators and planning tools provided by WHealth Calculator, including but not limited to the EMI Calculator, SIP Calculator, Retirement Planner, Financial Portfolio Planner, and other investment-related calculators, are mathematical simulation models intended solely for educational and informational purposes. They illustrate estimated scenarios based on the information provided by users and do not guarantee actual investment returns, loan approvals, financial performance, or future market outcomes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-mute leading-relaxed font-semibold">
        WHealth Calculator is not a registered financial adviser, investment broker, or portfolio manager and does not provide personalized financial, investment, tax, or legal advice. Always consult a qualified financial professional or a SEBI-registered investment adviser before making financial or investment decisions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="font-sans text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">4. Accuracy of Calculations</h2>
      <p>
        We strive to provide reliable calculations using widely accepted formulas and methodologies. However, WHealth Calculator does not warrant or guarantee that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-mute">
        <li>Every calculation is completely accurate or free from errors.</li>
        <li>Every recommendation is suitable for every individual.</li>
        <li>Every result is complete, current, or applicable to your specific circumstances.</li>
        <li>Calculator outputs will precisely reflect real-world outcomes.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
